Description: pi-topOS LXDE UI Customisations
 Customised theme and configuration for LXDE desktop on Raspberry Pi. Inherited
 from raspberrypi-ui-mods, this package uses 'LXDE-pt' instead of 'LXDE-pi'
 lxsession ID. This ensures that changes to 'raspberrypi-ui-mods' do not affect
 the UI of pi-topOS.
